{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "id": "寻狗_街头闲话",
  "entry": "root",
  "meta": {
    "title": "寻狗Demo·①.5雾津街头·散落世界观闲话（碎片·孤立flavor）"
  },
  "nodes": {
    "root": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "在这儿站上一盏茶的工夫，半条街的闲账都往耳朵里钻——",
      "next": "l1"
    },
    "l1": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "洗衣婆娘"
      },
      "text": "张家媳妇昨夜又听见有人喊名字，没敢应。",
      "next": "l2"
    },
    "l2": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "歇脚脚夫"
      },
      "text": "阎王岭那片，最近又没了两个人。",
      "next": "l3",
      "portrait": {
        "slug": "npc_coolie_a_anim",
        "emotion": "calm"
      }
    },
    "l3": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "茶客"
      },
      "text": "义庄说捞上来的尸都换过衣，邪门得很。",
      "next": "l4"
    },
    "l4": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "卖菜的"
      },
      "text": "南门外地税局，上个月闹了一整宿的鬼。",
      "next": "l5"
    },
    "l5": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "过路人"
      },
      "text": "听说了吗？洋人要进山了。",
      "next": "out"
    },
    "out": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "只言片语，拼不出个整。可这地方，最近是有点不对劲。",
      "next": "mark"
    },
    "end1": {
      "type": "end"
    },
    "mark": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
            "sourceType": "dialogue",
            "sourceId": "寻狗_街头闲话",
            "signal": "jietou_xianhua_heard"
          }
        }
      ],
      "next": "end1"
    }
  }
}
